OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 02 JUN
OL,4,CCHANNELS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2001FFollowing the takeover of HTV by
OL,7,FCarlton in October 2000, HTV's on air
OL,8,Fbranding remained untouched for a
OL,9,Fnumber of months. Until now.
OL,10,
OL,11,FAdapted versions of the spinning hearts
OL,12,Fidents were aired for the first time
OL,13,Ftoday. The new ident sequences featured
OL,14,Fthe soundtrack from the Carlton idents
OL,15,Fused in the Midlands and London.
OL,16,
OL,17,FAnd whilst they opened with the same
OL,18,Fvisuals as the London/Midlands idents,
OL,19,Fthe initial animation transitioned to
OL,20,Fthe spinning hearts/HTV logo animation
OL,21,Ffrom the previous set of HTV idents.
OL,22,
OL,23,Sppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppppp
